ABOUT

This is a simple script to batch copy directories containing mp3's to a specified directory.

CHANGELOG

* Thur Jun 21, 2012 by divreg
  Added support for nested directories (e.g. ALBUMARTIST/ALBUM) 

INSTALLING

yum install git
cd /opt/vortexbox/
git clone https://github.com/divreg/move2mp3
chmod a+x /opt/vortexbox/move2mp3/move2mp3.sh

USAGE

e.g. 

/opt/vortexbox/move2mp3/move2mp3.sh /storage/music/flac /storage/music/mp3

BE SURE TO INCLUDE THE FULL PATHS!
